<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css"> <!-- Adjust the path to your CSS file -->
    <title><%= law.title %> - Details</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1><%= law.title %></h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="law-details">
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p><%= law.summary %></p>

            <h2>Detailed Information</h2>
            <p><%= law.details %></p>

            <h2>Key Points</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Applicable Fines:</strong> The fines for violations can range from INR 1,000 to INR 10,000, depending on the offense.</li>
                <li><strong>Legal Proceedings:</strong> Legal action may be initiated if the regulations are not followed.</li>
                <li><strong>Financial Assistance:</strong> Various government schemes provide financial help for those affected by or seeking compliance with this law.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Additional Resources</h2>
            <p>For more details or legal assistance, consult a legal expert or visit the official website for this law.</p>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <a href="/simple">Back to Search</a>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
